Corruptions not in the teaching per se but corruption arising out of m=
isinterpretation of the words over time. One cannot really blame them for t=
his because it is almost impossible to forsee what turn of events lead to w=
hat kind of mindsets which can make their statements/advises defuct or even=
 dangerous over time.</DIV>
