<DIV>Shanakara, the great man t=
hat he was, would have died of a heart attack if he saw the flippant way in=
 which we later day college educated Indians use the phrases like Aham=
 Brahmasmi and everything is Brahman as if we are speaking about the latest=
 movie in town.  Also I feel his misjudged certain paths like Tantra.<=
/DIV>
